{"tid":1924323,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊千嬅取消吉隆坡演出　赴澳洲旅行與同陳小春一家「避炎」","createTime":"2020-03-13T15:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T16:24:48.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"114c41b39d294a19fc3ceda9bf4aa1bcda402300","tid":1924323,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"受到新冠肺炎影響，不少公眾活動被取消，比如演唱會。近日，宣布取消吉隆封巡迴演唱會的楊千嬅，一家三口連同陳小春一家相約前往澳洲渡假「避炎」，懷孕6個月的應采兒穿上黑色鬆身衫。<br />\n<br />\n其實本來楊千嬅正在舉行巡迴演唱會，可是受疫情影響，原定的吉隆坡站演出將延期，今日主辦單位更宣布，基於場館檔期及各種不確定因素的影響，未能在今年內進行補場。<br />\n<br />\n昨日（3月12日），陳小春兒子Jasper的微博粉絲圍發放了一張照片，相片中見到陳小春一家外，還有楊千嬅一家三口。<br />\n<br />\n由於近日陳家正身處澳洲，相信千嬅一家飛到澳洲聯同好友，讓兒子們去「放電」散心，順道「避炎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvtUDYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvtUDYa.jpg&h=762d4de3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b515a4cfa5c4098bbc8aeb0be9198a0d289711f","tid":1924323,"uid":186431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"呢班人中晒肺炎啦,屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68679831545de7c76e1edcd538fcd9deb7cb2031","tid":1924323,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"湯漢斯都係喺澳洲中招"},{"pid":"9d29637874724a6dbd095ca94addb694702a3a2e","tid":1924323,"uid":19093,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"2家人全家最緊要有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ede6260356e3c45cbb0fdfc5618bb78182df548","tid":1924323,"uid":7452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"咁愛國唔返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9197eb5deedd41a6aa9c9726c9aa4bfb5fe3b9","tid":1924323,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"咁唔愛支？雜種都留喺支那好似係"},{"pid":"76faa666f79ded4287572a6e83a2cbfcf94e404c",